  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Xalet Verdú is offered on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Each morning a buffet breakfast with hot and cold options if served between 8 and 10.30am.</p>
<p>Dinner consists of three courses with a starter buffet then a choice of main course and dessert, served between 7:30 and 10pm</p>
<p>Christmas and New Years Gala dinners are included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
