  <description><![CDATA[<p>This attractive hotel is decorated in traditional Catalan style and offers tasteful and comfortable accommodation. You are sure to receive a warm welcome from the owners who provide a friendly and relaxing atmosphere for all guests.</p>
<h2>Fantastic location </h2>
<p>Hotel Xalet Verdú is located just 200 metres from the Arinsal gondola that takes you up to the main ski area and ski school meeting points, so you can really make the most of your time of the mountains. The hotel is located in the centre of Arinsal village with easy access to the capital Andorra la Vella, where you'll find a fantastic range of restaurants, bars and duty-free shopping. You'll also benefit from the location as the hotel placement offers incredible panoramic views of the village and the mountains.</p>
<h2>Food and drink </h2>
<p>The hotel has a coffee shop by day and bar by night, so you can enjoy a hot drink in the morning in preparation for the slopes and a warming cocktail in preparation for bed at the end of the day. The restaurant offers freshness and quality through it's continental meals with buffet style starters and desserts and a selection of main courses served to your table. </p>
<h2>Friendly hotel</h2>
<p>With more than 20 years experience, Hotel Xalet Verdús main priority is to take care of you and your needs during your stay, offering the best service and personalised attention. The hosts are friendly and welcoming and are always happy to lend a helping hand to make sure your holiday goes as smoothly as possible.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
